<h5 id="subject_1078263">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=120911.msg1078263#msg1078263" rel="nofollow">Re: 【安科】用各种TRPG规则里的角色来当从者打一架如何？</a>
